<!doctype html>
<html lang="pl">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="icon" href="data:," />
  <title>Procedure Lego — Minimal Per-Asset ML Pipeline (L1–L9 + guards)</title>
<!--
  ============================================================================
  PROCEDURE LEGO · aplikacja 1-plikowa (zero zależności/builda)
  Minimalny per-asset pipeline S&P 500: warstwy L1–L9 + guardy G.1–G.3 +
  ciągły search plane S.1 + pochodny dashboard D.1 w 5 torach. POCHODNA SOT: treść klocków = bloki
  "Kontrakt replikacji" w Project/endproduct/Layers_Short_SOT.md (przy
  rozbieżności wygrywa SOT). Liczby data-state + config renderowane przez
  Project/Structure/config/data_state_numbers_gate.py (tokeny {{...}} w .tmpl);
  edytuj .tmpl, potem `make build` w Project/Structure — nigdy wygenerowanego .html.

  MAPA DLA AGENTÓW — edytuj we właściwej sekcji:
    CSS  [S1] tokeny kolorów      [S2] layout (workspace/panele)
         [S3] inventory (lewy)    [S4] canvas + klocki + separatory + sticky nagłówki torów
         [S5] wizualizacje (viz)  [S6] inspector (prawy)  [S7] toast/media
         [S8] modal + FAB (dodawanie klocka / potwierdzenie przeniesienia)
    JS   [J1] DANE   — GROUPS + MODULES (kontrakty procedur; SOT tej apki)
         [J1b] PROMPTS — prompty replikacyjne PL (decyzje + best practices)
         [J2] VIZ    — rejestr mini-wizualizacji: 1 klucz = 1 rodzaj klocka
         [J3] LAYOUT — drabinka dół→góra z ORDER; wymiary canvas pochodne
         [J4] STATE  — localStorage v2 (order / custom)
         [J5] ORDER+DND — statyczne depends + insert-with-shift (wskaźnik wstawiania)
         [J6] CANVAS — render klocków, sticky nagłówki, pan/zoom, drag&drop
         [J7] INVENTORY + INSPECTOR — panele boczne, prompt replikacyjny
         [J9] MODAL+CUSTOM — okno „+" (submitAddBlock) + edycja (klik w .selected-id
              → openEditModal/submitEditBlock, tylko custom) + potwierdzenie ruchu
              (openMoveModal) + custom-moduły (v2.custom, isCustom/deleteCustomBlock)
         [J8] BOOT   — start

  JAK DODAĆ MODUŁ — dwie ścieżki:
  (1) trwale: dopisz obiekt do MODULES (kolejność = przepływ dół→góra) i wskaż
      viz z rejestru VIZ (lub dodaj nowy wpis w VIZ: {h, render}).
  (2) w aplikacji: przycisk „+" (lewy-górny róg canvasu) → modal → klocek
      zapisany w localStorage v2.custom, kasowalny przez „USUŃ KLOCEK" w inspectorze.
  Tory, separatory, nagłówki i wysokość canvas wyliczają się same; nowy moduł
  ląduje na szczycie drabinki — przeciągnij go na miejsce (modal potwierdzi ruch).
  ============================================================================
-->
  <style>
    /* [S1] tokeny */
    :root{
      --bg-root:#080A0D;
      --bg-panel:#0D1117;
      --line:#27303A;
      --line-soft:#1B232C;
      --text:#E8EDF2;
      --muted:#89929D;
      --amber:#FFA028;
      --green:#44D17A;
      --red:#FF5C6C;
      --cyan:#54B8FF;
      /* paleta semantyczna wizualizacji (wg TEST.html: rola → kolor) */
      --v-src:#ABA99F;      /* source / acquisition */
      --v-store:#2BB587;    /* store / artifact (teal) */
      --v-green:#86B23A;    /* transform */
      --v-amber:#D89A3A;    /* gate / control / OOS */
      --v-good:#34C96A;     /* wynik / TP / endproduct */
      --v-fail:#F26B6A;     /* błąd / SL / purge */
      --v-blue:#5CB0FF;     /* embargo / README */
      --v-pink:#E673A3;     /* Risk-Box / notebook */
      --v-gray:#8a8980;     /* świece / neutralne */
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{height:100%;min-width:1024px}
    body{margin:0;background:var(--bg-root);color:var(--text);font:12px/1.35 ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Consolas,monospace;overflow:hidden}
    button,input{font:inherit}
    button{border:0;background:transparent;color:var(--text);padding:0;cursor:pointer}
    button:hover{color:var(--amber)}
    button:focus-visible{outline:1px solid var(--amber);outline-offset:-1px}

    /* [S2] layout */
    .terminal{height:100vh;display:grid;grid-template-rows:minmax(0,1fr);background:var(--line);gap:1px}
    .workspace{display:grid;grid-template-columns:18% minmax(0,1fr) 24%;gap:1px;min-height:0;background:var(--line)}
    .panel{min-width:0;min-height:0;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--bg-panel)}

    /* [S3] inventory */
    .inventory-controls{padding:7px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;gap:4px;flex-wrap:wrap}
    .filter{font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);padding:3px 5px;border:1px solid transparent}
    .filter.active{color:var(--amber);border-color:var(--amber)}
    .module-list{overflow:auto;min-height:0;padding:5px 0}
    .inventory-group{padding:5px 7px 3px;color:var(--muted);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.08em;border-top:1px solid var(--line-soft)}
    .inventory-group:first-child{border-top:0}
    .inventory-row{height:28px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:33px 1fr;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:0 8px;cursor:grab;border-left:3px solid transparent;color:#C7D0D8}
    .inventory-row:hover,.inventory-row.selected{background:#111820;color:var(--text)}
    .inventory-row.selected{border-left-color:var(--amber)}
    .inventory-id{font-size:10px;color:var(--text)}
    .inventory-name{font-size:10px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}

    /* [S4] canvas + klocki */
    .flow-panel{position:relative}
    .flow-viewport{position:relative;overflow:hidden;flex:1;background-color:var(--bg-root);background-image:linear-gradient(var(--line-soft) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(--line-soft) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:20px 20px}
    .flow-canvas{position:relative;width:1400px;height:2600px;transform-origin:0 0;will-change:transform;cursor:grab} /* wymiary nadpisuje [J8] BOOT z CANVAS_W/H */
    .flow-canvas.panning{cursor:grabbing}
    .flow-canvas.drag-over{box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px var(--amber)}
    .lane-sep{position:absolute;top:0;bottom:0;width:1px;background:var(--line);pointer-events:none} /* szerokość kompensuje zoom applyTransform */
    .insert-line{position:absolute;background:var(--amber);box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(255,160,40,.45);pointer-events:none;z-index:9}
    /* sticky nagłówki torów — warstwa viewportu (poza transformacją), stała wielkość ekranowa */
    .lane-heads{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:26px;pointer-events:none;z-index:8;overflow:hidden}
    .lane-head{position:absolute;top:0;height:26px;line-height:26px;padding:0 4px;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--bg-root) 30%,rgba(8,10,13,.72) 65%,transparent)}

    .lego{position:absolute;width:184px;background:#0D1117;border:1px solid #46515D;border-left:4px solid var(--accent);padding:15px 8px 6px;cursor:grab;user-select:none;box-shadow:4px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.18);transition:top .15s ease,left .15s ease}
    .lego:active{cursor:grabbing}
    .lego:hover{border-color:#8A96A3;z-index:5}
    .lego.selected{outline:1px solid var(--amber);outline-offset:2px;z-index:6}
    .studs{position:absolute;top:-5px;left:9px;display:flex;gap:7px}
    .stud{width:13px;height:5px;border:1px solid var(--accent);border-bottom:0;background:#161D25}
    .lego-top{display:flex;gap:7px;align-items:baseline}
    .lego-id{color:var(--accent);font-size:10px;font-weight:800}
    .lego-title{font-size:10px;color:var(--text);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;font-weight:700}
    /* [S5] wizualizacje — wspólne */
    .viz-svg{display:block;width:100%;height:auto;margin-top:5px}
    .viz-label{margin-top:6px;text-align:center;font-size:8px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.05em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
    .viz-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;table-layout:fixed;margin-top:5px}
    .viz-tbl th,.viz-tbl td{border:1px solid var(--line);text-align:center;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap}
    .viz-tbl th{height:13px;font-size:7px;font-weight:800;color:var(--text);background:rgba(255,255,255,.05)}
    .viz-tbl td{height:12px;font-size:6.5px;color:#9AA4AE}
    .ohlcv-x{font-size:1.5em;font-weight:800;vertical-align:-1px;margin-right:1px}
    /* 1.2 · łańcuch ZIP (LEAN, 1 zip = 1 ticker) */
    .zip-chain{margin-top:6px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:center;gap:3px}
    .zip-node{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px}
    .zip-box{width:28px;height:19px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:9px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--accent);background:rgba(85,199,164,.12);border:1px solid var(--accent);border-radius:2px}
    .zip-tk{font-size:7px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.03em;color:var(--muted)}
    .zip-dot{flex:0 0 auto;width:4px;height:4px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);opacity:.55;margin-top:7px}
    .zip-ell{flex:0 0 auto;color:var(--accent);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:1px;opacity:.7;margin-top:4px}
    /* 1.3 · checklista QC źródła */
    .qc-list{margin-top:6px;display:grid;gap:2px}
    .qc-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:42px 1fr 10px;align-items:center;font-size:7.5px;color:#9AA4AE}
    .qc-row b{color:var(--text);font-weight:800}
    .qc-ok{color:var(--v-good);font-weight:800;justify-self:end}
    /* 2.2 · macierz cech — narożnik x/t */
    .xt{position:relative;background:linear-gradient(to top right,transparent 47%,#46515D 47%,#46515D 53%,transparent 53%)!important}
    .xt .x{position:absolute;top:0;right:2px;font-size:6px}
    .xt .t{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:2px;font-size:6px}
    .th-x{color:var(--v-green)!important;background:rgba(134,178,58,.14)!important}
    .th-y{color:var(--v-good)!important;background:rgba(52,201,106,.20)!important}
    td.y1{background:rgba(52,201,106,.22);color:var(--v-good)!important;font-weight:800}
    td.y0{color:var(--muted)!important}
    /* 2.4 · bramka jakości */
    .gate{margin-top:8px;display:flex;gap:5px;justify-content:center}
    .gate-chip{border:1px solid;padding:3px 7px;font-size:9px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.04em}
    .gate-chip.ok{color:var(--v-good);border-color:var(--v-good);background:rgba(52,201,106,.12);box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(52,201,106,.35)}
    .gate-chip.warn{color:var(--v-amber);border-color:var(--v-amber);opacity:.5}
    .gate-chip.fail{color:var(--v-fail);border-color:var(--v-fail);opacity:.5}
    .gate-note{margin-top:6px;text-align:center;font-size:7.5px;color:var(--muted)}
    .gate-note b{color:var(--v-good)}
    /* 3.1 · macierz triali Optuny */
    .viz-tbl td.o-best,.viz-tbl th.o-best{background:rgba(216,154,58,.16);color:var(--v-amber)}
    .viz-tbl tr.o-auc td{background:rgba(52,201,106,.10);color:var(--v-good)}
    .viz-tbl td.o-name{text-align:left;padding-left:3px;color:#C7D0D8}
    .viz-tbl td.st-p{color:var(--v-fail)}.viz-tbl td.st-b{color:var(--v-good);font-weight:800}
    /* 3.2 · linia budowy artefaktu */
    .build{margin-top:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:3px}
    .b-arr{color:var(--v-amber);font-size:9px;font-weight:800}
    .b-chip{border:1px solid;border-radius:2px;padding:3px 4px;font-size:6.5px;font-weight:800;white-space:nowrap}
    .b-json{color:var(--v-green);border-color:var(--v-green);background:rgba(134,178,58,.10)}
    .b-xgb{color:#fff;border-color:var(--v-store);background:rgba(29,158,117,.35);font-size:8px;padding:3px 6px}
    .b-b64{color:var(--v-store);border-color:var(--v-store);background:rgba(29,158,117,.10);font-size:5.8px}
    .b-py{color:var(--v-good);border-color:var(--v-good);background:rgba(52,201,106,.10)}
    .build-sub{margin-top:4px;text-align:center;font-size:6.5px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
    /* 4.2 · legenda plików folderu */
    .f-legend{margin-top:3px;display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:7px;font-size:6.5px;font-weight:700}

    /* [S6] inspector */
    .inspector-content{overflow:auto;min-height:0}
    .empty-state{padding:14px;color:var(--muted);font-size:10px;line-height:1.55}
    .selected-strip{padding:9px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:grid;grid-template-columns:38px 1fr;gap:8px;align-items:center}
    .selected-id{color:var(--bg-root);background:var(--amber);font-weight:900;font-size:11px;text-align:center;padding:4px 2px}
    .selected-name{font-size:11px;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2}
    .selected-kind{font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}
    .inspect-section{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:9px}
    .inspect-label{color:var(--amber);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.09em;margin-bottom:6px}
    .inspect-text{font-size:10px;color:#C9D1D9;line-height:1.5}
    .inspect-list{margin:0;padding:0;list-style:none;display:grid;gap:4px}
    .inspect-list li{font-size:10px;color:#C9D1D9;line-height:1.4}
    .inspect-list li::before{content:'›';color:var(--amber);margin-right:6px}
    .knob-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-left:1px solid var(--line)}
    .knob{min-width:0;padding:6px;border-right:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
    .knob b{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:8px;font-weight:400;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
    .knob span{display:block;margin-top:3px;color:var(--text);font-size:9px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
    /* akordeon promptu replikacyjnego */
    .prompt-acc summary{list-style:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:var(--amber);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.09em;cursor:pointer;user-select:none}
    .prompt-acc summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
    .prompt-acc summary i{font-style:normal;transition:transform .15s}
    .prompt-acc[open] summary i{transform:rotate(90deg)}
    .prompt-bar{display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;margin:8px 0 6px}
    .prompt-bar button{color:var(--cyan);font-size:10px}
    .prompt-bar button:hover{color:var(--amber)}
    .prompt-pre{margin:0;background:#0A0E13;border:1px solid var(--line);padding:8px;font-size:10px;line-height:1.5;color:#C9D1D9;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-word;max-height:340px;overflow:auto}
    /* powiększona kopia viz w inspectorze */
    .viz-card{margin-top:2px;background:#0D1117;border:1px solid #46515D;border-left:4px solid var(--accent);padding:13px;overflow:hidden}
    .viz-card .viz-tbl th{height:18px;font-size:10px}
    .viz-card .viz-tbl td{height:16px;font-size:9px}
    .viz-card .viz-label{font-size:10px;margin-top:9px}
    .viz-card .qc-row{font-size:10px;grid-template-columns:64px 1fr 14px}
    .viz-card .gate-chip{font-size:12px;padding:5px 12px}
    .viz-card .gate-note,.viz-card .build-sub{font-size:9.5px}
    .viz-card .b-chip{font-size:9px;padding:5px 7px}
    .viz-card .b-b64{font-size:8px}.viz-card .b-xgb{font-size:11px}
    .viz-card .f-legend{font-size:9px;gap:12px}
    .viz-card .xt .x,.viz-card .xt .t{font-size:9px}
    .viz-card .zip-box{width:36px;height:24px;font-size:11px}
    .viz-card .zip-tk{font-size:9px}
    .viz-card .zip-dot{width:5px;height:5px;margin-top:11px}
    .viz-card .zip-ell{margin-top:8px}

    /* [S7] toast + media */
    .toast{position:fixed;bottom:24px;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,45px);opacity:0;pointer-events:none;border:1px solid var(--amber);background:#0B1016;color:var(--amber);padding:6px 9px;font-size:10px;z-index:60;transition:.16s}
    .toast.show{opacity:1;transform:translate(-50%,0)}
    @media(max-width:1180px){html,body{min-width:900px}.workspace{grid-template-columns:190px minmax(500px,1fr) 240px}.inventory-name{font-size:9px}}

    /* [S8] modal + FAB — okno „+" (dodaj klocek, F1) + potwierdzenie ruchu (F2) */
    .add-fab{position:absolute;top:8px;left:8px;z-index:12;width:26px;height:26px;border:1px solid var(--amber);background:var(--bg-panel);color:var(--amber);font-size:17px;font-weight:800;line-height:22px;text-align:center;box-shadow:2px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.35);cursor:pointer}
    .add-fab:hover{background:var(--amber);color:var(--bg-root)}
    .add-fab:focus-visible{outline:1px solid var(--amber);outline-offset:2px}
    .modal-overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:100;background:rgba(8,10,13,.72);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px}
    .modal-overlay[hidden]{display:none} /* konieczne — display:flex bije UA [hidden] */
    .modal{width:min(560px,92vw);max-height:88vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--bg-panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-top:3px solid var(--amber);box-shadow:6px 6px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.45)}
    .modal-head{padding:12px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--amber);font-size:12px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
    .modal-body{padding:12px 14px;display:grid;gap:9px;overflow:auto}
    .modal-foot{padding:11px 14px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;gap:8px}
    .modal-grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:9px}
    .modal-field{display:grid;gap:3px;border:1px solid transparent;border-radius:2px;padding:5px 6px}
    .modal-field>label{font-size:9px;color:var(--muted);letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase}
    .modal-field:focus-within{border-color:var(--amber);background:rgba(255,160,40,.05)} /* highlight aktywnego pola */
    .modal-field.err{border-color:var(--red)}
    .modal-field.err>label{color:var(--red)}
    .modal-field .err-msg{font-size:8.5px;color:var(--red)}
    .modal input,.modal select,.modal textarea{width:100%;background:var(--bg-root);border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--text);font:inherit;padding:5px 6px;outline:none}
    .modal input:focus,.modal select:focus,.modal textarea:focus{border-color:var(--amber)}
    .modal input[readonly]{color:var(--muted);cursor:not-allowed}
    .modal textarea{resize:vertical;min-height:44px;line-height:1.4}
    .modal-btn{border:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent;color:var(--text);padding:6px 14px;font:inherit;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.05em;cursor:pointer}
    .modal-btn:hover{border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber)}
    .modal-btn.primary{border-color:var(--amber);color:var(--amber)}
    .modal-btn.primary:hover{background:var(--amber);color:var(--bg-root)}
    .move-summary{font-size:11px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7}
    .move-summary b{color:var(--amber)}
    .move-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;margin:0 3px;padding:4px 9px;border:1px solid var(--amber);color:var(--amber);background:rgba(255,160,40,.10);font-weight:800;box-shadow:0 0 9px rgba(255,160,40,.55)}
    .del-wrap{padding:9px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
    .del-block{width:100%;padding:7px;border:1px solid var(--red);background:transparent;color:var(--red);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.06em;cursor:pointer}
    .del-block:hover{background:var(--red);color:var(--bg-root)}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="terminal">
    <section class="workspace">
      <aside class="panel inventory">
        <div class="inventory-controls" id="filters"></div>
        <div class="module-list" id="moduleList"></div>
      </aside>

      <section class="panel flow-panel">
        <div class="flow-viewport" id="flowViewport">
          <div class="flow-canvas" id="flowCanvas" aria-label="Drag and drop procedure canvas">
            <div class="insert-line" id="insertLine" hidden></div>
          </div>
          <div class="lane-heads" id="laneHeads" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          <button class="add-fab" id="addFab" title="Dodaj klocek" aria-label="Dodaj nowy klocek">+</button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class="panel inspector">
        <div class="inspector-content" id="inspectorContent"></div>
      </aside>
    </section>
  </main>
  <div class="toast" id="toast"></div>
  <div class="modal-overlay" id="modalOverlay" hidden>
    <div class="modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="modalTitle">
      <div class="modal-head" id="modalTitle"></div>
      <div class="modal-body" id="modalBody"></div>
      <div class="modal-foot" id="modalFoot"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    'use strict';
    /* ==================================================================
